Simple tool to benchmark sites (rpm, response time, etc)

Use like this:
./nethttperf.rb -n 100 -c 3 http://www.yoursite.com

Options:
  --concurrent-threads, -c <i>:   Number of concurrent threads (default: 3)
            --requests, -n <i>:   Total number of requests (default: 10)
                           url:   Url to perform benchmarking on (default: http://localhost:3000/)
